quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Min nulii Nuuhu haa e yim…ďe makko …ďeen, won'de : ""Jeertin yim…ďe ma …ďen, ado lette mu'usuu…óe arde e ma…ď…ďe""."
  71,2,"O maakani […ďe] : ""ehey yim…ďe am, miin ko mi jeertinoowo on …ďanngu…óo."
  71,3,"won'de yo on ndewu Allah, kulon mo, …óofto…óon kam."
  71,4,"O haforanat on bakkatuuji i mon …óin, O nee…ďna on haa e lajal ta∆īaangal. [Ko woni tan] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal nee…ďnetaake, si tawii ho…óon nganndunoo!""."
  71,5,"O maaki : ""Joomi am, miin mi noddirii yim…ďe am …ďeen jehma e √Īalawma,"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am nduun …ďeydaani …ďe, si wonaa dogugol."
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi …ďe fii no kafaranaa …ďe, …ďe mba…óat kolli ma…ď…ďe …óiin ka ndeer noppi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe buumora comci ma…ď…ďe …óiin, …ďe deppitoo, …ďe townitora townitaadee."
  71,8,"Refti mi noddirii …ďe e kene.(Fee√Īi)."
  71,9,"Refti mi fe√Ī√Īinani …ďe, mi suu…óanii …ďe suu…óaandee."
  71,10,"Mi wi'i […ďe] : ""Imsinanee Joomi mon, tawde o siforii won'de kaforoowo."
  71,11,"O wurtira to…ďo ngo e mon dewnindiral,"
  71,12,"O …ďeydira on jaw…óe e …ďi…ó…ďe, o wa…óana on gese, o wa…óana on caatli."
  71,13,"E ko he…ďi on, on njoortaaki manngural Allah ngal,"
  71,14,"Jojji o tagir on taa…ďe-taa…ďe?"
  71,15,"E on nji'ataa no Allah tagiri kammuuji jee…ói…ói tegondir…ói?"
  71,16,"O wa…ói lewru ndun jal…ďundu e majji, o wa…ói na'ange ngen pitilol."
  71,17,"Ko Allah fu…óniri on ka lesdi pu…ónugol."
  71,18,"Refti o ruttirat on e mayri, o yaltina on yaltinndee."
  71,19,"Allah wa…óiranii on leydi ndiin weertaandi."
  71,20,"fii yo on naatir e mayri laabi jaac…ói""."
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : ""Joomi am, …ďee njeddii kam, …ďe njokkii on mo jaw…óe mum e …ďi…ó…ďe …ďeydaani …óum si wonaa hayrugol."
  71,22,"∆Āe pewji fehre mawnde."
  71,23,"…ďe mbi'i: ""Wota on terto dey dewetee…ói mon …óiin: wota on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr""."
  71,24,"Ko pellet, …ďe majjinii ko …óuu…ói. [Joomi] wota A …ďeydir too√Ī…ďe …ďeen, si wonaa majjere."
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi ma…ď…ďe …óiin …ďe njooliranoo, …ďe naatna Yiite, …ďe he…ďanaano ko'e ma…ď…ďe paabotoo…óo ga Allah""."
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : ""Joomi am, wota a accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo."
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si a accii …ďe, …ďe majjinat jiyaa…ďe maa …ďen, …ďe njibinoytaako si wonaa bonnoo…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe jeddi."
  71,28,"Joomi am, kaforanam miin e jibin…ďe kam …ďen, e …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe naatu…ďe ka suudu am, e gooŇč…óin…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gooŇč…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen; wata A …ďeydir too√Īu…ďe …ďeen, si wonaa halakuyee."
